00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:37,580
Sister.

147
00:11:37,580 --> 00:11:38,500
What are you doing?

148
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:41,340
Stuff for the wedding.

149
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:44,100
Didn't Marshal say

150
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:45,420
