158
00:12:10,180 --> 00:12:11,220
It doesn't hurt. I'm fine.

159
00:12:12,820 --> 00:12:13,820
It doesn't hurt?

160
00:12:13,860 --> 00:12:15,060
I know you too well.

161
00:12:15,060 --> 00:12:16,340
You can't bear any pain.

162
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:17,860
