216
00:15:41,820 --> 00:15:43,100
Leave now.

217
00:15:43,220 --> 00:15:44,300
It's dangerous.

218
00:15:45,100 --> 00:15:46,330
Young man,

219
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:48,060
It's dark and windy.

220
00:15:48,180 --> 00:15:49,340
If I leave,

221
00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:51,180
