223
00:15:55,570 --> 00:15:57,340
It's not bad

224
00:15:58,980 --> 00:16:00,300
to be suspended in a tree.

225
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:01,700
Are you sure?

226
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:04,740
There's a forest here.

227
00:16:05,450 --> 00:16:06,420
Over there,

228
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:08,700
