280
00:18:42,940 --> 00:18:44,220
Wangyue and I

281
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:47,620
truly love each other.

282
00:18:52,620 --> 00:18:54,300
Complete your mission well.

283
00:18:55,470 --> 00:18:57,140
