284
00:18:57,300 --> 00:18:58,660
those lunatic ravings you said.

285
00:19:03,620 --> 00:19:04,500
Yin,

286
00:19:05,060 --> 00:19:06,380
I can't be

287
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:08,220
