00:34:22,139 --> 00:34:23,820
Okay, get up.

579
00:34:23,969 --> 00:34:24,460
Come on.

580
00:34:28,260 --> 00:34:33,340
♫I'm still looking for you until the falling flowers return with spring♫

581
00:34:31,980 --> 00:34:32,900
I wish you

582
00:34:33,260 --> 00:34:34,540
