00:36:11,420 --> 00:36:12,540
Well,

621
00:36:12,810 --> 00:36:14,060
After winning the battle

622
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:15,420
and return to the capital,

623
00:36:15,460 --> 00:36:16,260
do you

624
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:17,980
