628
00:36:22,940 --> 00:36:23,580
Good.

629
00:36:24,020 --> 00:36:26,100
What a loser.

630
00:36:26,100 --> 00:36:26,980
Good.

631
00:36:27,460 --> 00:36:29,820
It's not easy for you

632
00:36:30,250 --> 00:36:31,620
